{"word":"H3444 - יְשׁוּעָה - yᵉshûwʻâh - yesh-oo'-aw - Deliverance","slug":"H3444","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יְשׁוּעָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yᵉshûwʻâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yesh-oo'-aw"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Deliverance"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E2;&#x05D4; - y<sup>e</sup>shu&#x0302;&#x201B;a&#x0302;h</b> - <i>yesh-oo'-aw</i><p/>Feminine passive participle of <a href=\"#/H3467\">H3467</a>; something <i>saved</i>, that is, (abstractly) <i>deliverance</i>; hence <i>aid</i>, <i>victory</i>, <i>prosperity: - </i>deliverance, health, help (-ing), salvation, save, saving (health), welfare."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1954\">H1954</a>, <a href=\"#/H1955\">H1955</a>, <a href=\"#/H3467\">H3467</a>, <a href=\"#/H3468\">H3468</a>, <a href=\"#/H3469\">H3469</a>, <a href=\"#/H3470\">H3470</a>, <a href=\"#/H3471\">H3471</a>, <a href=\"#/H4190\">H4190</a>, <a href=\"#/H4337\">H4337</a>, <a href=\"#/H4338\">H4338</a>, <a href=\"#/H7769\">H7769</a>, <a href=\"#/H7770\">H7770</a>, <a href=\"#/H7771\">H7771</a>, <a href=\"#/H7774\">H7774</a>, <a href=\"#/H8668\">H8668</a>"}]}